lead_paragraph: James Harden was called for one of the eight technicals in a game that turned tense when Dallas center Andrew Bogut received a flagrant foul on a hard screen that staggered Houston's star guard.

headline.print_headline: Harden Calls Out Mavs After Rockets' Tech-Marred 123-107 Win
